summary: SIDEWALL SEPERATION WAS DISCOVERED ON 9/22/17ON AN INSTALLED IRONMAN TRAILER TIRE. TIRE WAS PURCHASED AND INSTALLED ON 4/18/15 BY FIRESTONE TIRES IN SURPRISE AZ. THE VEHICLE IS A SMALL 2 HORSE TRAILER THAT ONLY SEES OCCASIONAL USE SO VERY LITTLE TREAD WEAR. TRAILER WAS PARKED AT THE TIME OF DISCOVERY.
